headline: Should You Forget Coca-Cola? Why These Unstoppable Stocks Are Better Buys.
summary: Coca-Cola is a Dividend King and an industry-leading beverage giant, but its stock price is a bit expensive today.  Hormel is also a Dividend King, and the stock appears cheap.  Hershey is an industry leader in the confectionery space, and the stock looks cheap.
